The fourth is a Type III secretion system protein SpaR. The fifth is a Type III secretion system protein SpaO. The sixth is a Type III secretion system protein SpaS. The seventh is a FecR protein domain protein. The eighth is a O-acetylhomoserine sulfhydrylase.
